wr-cgl
======

This layer provides the Carrier Grade components for Wind River Linux.  It
requires the wr-base layer, provided by Wind River. Additionally, it requires
the wr-security layer packaged in the addons tree.


Dependencies
------------
This layer depends on the following layers:
  openembedded-core
  meta-networking
  meta-selinux
  wr-base
  wr-kernel
  wr-security
  wr-template

The layer also recommends the following layers:
  wrlinux
  wr-cgl-dl

Maintenance
-----------
This layer is maintained by Wind River Systems, Inc.
Contact <support@windriver.com> or your support representative for more
information on submitting changes.


Building the wr-cgl layer
-------------------------
This layer should be added to the bblayers.conf file.  This is done
automatically when using the Wind River configure wrapper.


